rashida = Agent.create(first_name: "Rashida", last_name: "Perez, MBA", biography: "Originally from Altadena, California, Rashida moved to San Francisco California to pursue her Bachelor’s degree in Psychology from San Francisco State University. Upon completion of her degree program in 1999, she moved to Ventura California and pursued her Master’s Degree in Business Administration from the University of Phoenix which she completed in 2003.
