property1 = Property.create(address: "1341 Edgewood Way #23", city: "Oxnard", state: "CA", zip: "93030", price: 225000, sold: "true", transaction_date: "2019-06-28", client: "Seller", bed: 2, bath: 1, sqft: 1101, description: "Welcome home to this spectacular, spacious, top floor, end unit condo. Located in a quaint gated complex in desirable North Oxnard. This home boast over 1,100 square feet of living space, 2 bedrooms and 1 HUGE master bath. Full size interior laundry, large living room with a balcony and fireplace, light and bright kitchen with dining area. The master bedroom features an en-suite bath, large closet and private balcony. Home also features a detached garage. A rare gem in this community! HOA includes, water, trash, master insurance, gated community, community pool and all exterior maintenance. Located within walking distance to shops, schools, park, restaurants and public transportation. Complex is approved for VA financing.")
property2 = Property.create(address: "1388 Strawberry Hill Rd", city: "Thousand Oaks", state: "CA", zip: "91360", price: 782500, sold: "true", transaction_date: "2019-04-09", client: "Buyer-Seller", bed: 3, bath: 2, sqft: 1898, description: "First time on the market! One of the first custom built estates on the street and original owners! This spacious ranch home, boasts 1898 sq. ft., 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, on a level .45 acre lot zoned for equestrian use. The home also has plenty of RV parking and is located in the desirable Westgate Estates in the heart of Thousand Oaks. As you drive up to this sprawling property you are greeted with something very special. Features inside the home include two beautiful wood burning brick fireplaces, original hardwood floors, ceiling fans in all bedrooms, new recess lighting in the large eat-in kitchen and French doors off the master bedroom and den that each open up to separate patio areas. Close to the freeway, award winning schools, shopping, restaurants, the hospital, equestrian trails/center. This is a rare beauty in Thousand Oaks and won't last long!")
