property8 = Property.create(address: "3886 Germain St", city: "Camarillo", state: "CA", zip: "93010", price: 556000, sold: "true", transaction_date: "2017-02-02", client: "Seller", bed: 4, bath: 2, sqft: 1530, description: "This 4 bedroom 2 bathroom (recently remodeled) + office home sits on a large corner lot with Rv parking. The recently landscaped backyard includes beautiful palm trees and tropical plants on a drip system, salt water hot tub, covered patio, BBQ area, custom built concrete slab wooden shed, vegetable garden, and large grass area with play set. Remodeled open kitchen with breakfast bar/peninsula. Plantation shutters throughout, vaulted ceiling, fireplace in living room. AIR CONDITIONING is so nice to have and this house has it!")
