janell.testimonials << Testimonial.create(comment: "Janell was incredibly helpful, responsive and knowledgeable.  My fiancee and I were looking for rental properties in Ventura County for some time, and had been working with other agents, but no one took the time and put in the effort like Janell.  Within a couple weeks of looking Janell found us a  property within our budget for us and our kids.  Janell is personable and communicative.  Even though we weren't buying she treated us like were a priority.  We really appreciate the help Janell!  You are fantastic!", source: "Zillow", client: "chris haines24")
janell.testimonials << Testimonial.create(comment: "Everything went great, I will definitely call her for my next home buying ! Buying a home for the first time can be scary. Janell was very knowledgeable and explained the process so I could understand how it works and protect yourself in the process. I am very Happy !!!", source: "Zillow", client: "wirehead5054")
janell.testimonials << Testimonial.create(comment: "Janell is such a pleasure to work with. She is a hard worker and dedicated to her clients. She is easy to get along with and is willing to get in there and fight for you when needed. I look forward to working with her in the future!", source: "Zillow", client: "user44637817")
janell.testimonials << Testimonial.create(comment: "Janell Case-McCallion from Ventana Properties helped me successfully sell and purchase an incredible home in Camarillo, Ca. She was patient, very flexible, and super quick to respond to my questions. She's a personable, competent and confident women and I felt comfortable with her immediately.  Janell gave great advice as far as my offer went- she was very knowledgeable about what would make our offer stand out in an extremely challenging market. She helped me view the place several times, get it pre-inspected, get my mortgage details in order, put the offer together, and beat out two other offers, all in less than a week. The seller’s realtor complimented Janell work on the offer package, saying it was unusually detailed and that he was a pleasure for her to work with. This was my second home buying experience, and Janell made it as anxiety- free as possible. I really thank her for being so quick and responsive, so we got to land our perfect forever home! I would recommend Janell and Ventana Properties to all my family and friends.", source: "Zillow", client: "dcase128")
rashida.testimonials << Testimonial.create(comment: "Rashida is AMAZING! She assisted me with buying my very first house. It was such a pleasant experience working with Rashida. She was very attentive in answering all my questions. She consistently followed up with me and everyone involved in the process to ensure things continued to run smoothly. Absolutely any question I had, she answered! Throughout the entire process which for me was an emotional rollercoaster; she guided me and made me feel comfortable and confident in my decisions.  I was very thankful to have an understanding person like Rashida to help me throughout this process. AMAZING customer service! Thank you!", client: "Key’Shaun Lewis")
